column5: Ok we fished at lac seul for a week the 21-28 n every time they said it would be stormy it was about mid 80s then when it was suspose to be nice it was cold as #### and rainy. I just wondered if neone else notices this?
I was up on the Lac 3 wks ago and the reports seemed accurate. This is the site I use while in Green Bay to monitor the weather up there: http://weatheroffice.ec.gc.ca/forecast/city_e.html?yhd
